Paint Core Finishes is a custom refinishing company. We provide top-notch kitchen cabinet, vanity, woodwork and furniture re-spraying, refinishing and painting services in the GTA.

Reclaim your kitchen cabinets, vanities, and woodwork!

We believe in doing things right the first time. We specialize in the fine art of cabinet refinishing, painting, re-spraying and wood finishing. If you have a tired looking kitchen and are thinking of replacing it, think twice. We have salvaged hundreds of kitchens with our factory finish process. We pride ourselves on producing high quality finishes on all your existing cabinetry, millwork and furniture. By implementing a very thorough preparation, combined with the right application systems, topnotch equipment and coatings we provide amazing results. This is our recipe for success!

Our philosophy is that a refinished kitchen shouldnâ€™t look refinished; it should look like it was bought that way.

profile:
At The Wright Kitchen, we understand that your kitchen is the heart of your home and that no two kitchens are the same. We offer a complete line of high quality, affordable kitchen cabinets that can be specifically designed to make your space functional, efficient and beautiful. We work with homeowners from concept to completion and ensure that your renovation is as easy and inexpensive as possible.

Based in Burlington, Ontario, we provide kitchen, bath, basement and home entertainment cabinet solutions to surrounding areas including Brantford, Ancaster, Hamilton, Stoney Creek, St. Catherines, Oakville, Mississauga, Toronto, Kitchener Cambridge, Guelph and Waterloo. Please explore our site and contact us for a no-obligation consultation.

We invite you to visit us in our showroom at:

The Wright Kitchen
4087 Harvester Rd. Unit 3 & 4
Burlington, Ontario
L7L 5M3
905-639-1099
